                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Ma᾿azene ha-῾iyunim</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">מאזני העיונים</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/31996761">Ghazzālī</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/31996761">אלע'זאלי, מחמד בן מחמד</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>In the translation of Jacob ben Machir ibn Tibbon. The attribution of this work to Ghazzālī has been rejected by scholars, see <ref target="Da'at" type="number">34</ref> (1995), pp. 83-86. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
